# What this file is: a template for worker/.dev.vars (gitignored), the
# local secrets file `wrangler dev` reads. Copy this to .dev.vars and fill
# in a real key -- never commit .dev.vars itself.
# In plain terms: shows you what to put in your local secrets file to test
# the proxy against a real LLM.

LLM_API_KEY=your-groq-api-key-here
